    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Urgent: Addressing Attendance Concerns\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter that has come to our attention regarding your recent attendance. Over the past two weeks, you have been arriving approximately 15 minutes late to your shifts each day. While we understand that unforeseen circumstances can occasionally cause delays, consistent tardiness is impacting your performance and the overall efficiency of our team.\n\nWe value your contribution to our company and would like to remind you of the importance of punctuality in maintaining a productive work environment. We kindly request that you adhere to the scheduled start times for your shifts moving forward. If you foresee any challenges that may affect your punctuality, please communicate with your supervisor or HR representative promptly to discuss possible solutions. Please be aware that if this pattern of tardiness continues, it may result in more formal disciplinary action or a review of your employment status.\n\nWe appreciate your attention to this matter and your continued dedication to your role. Should you have any questions or require further clarification, please do not hesitate to reach out.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \nHR Manager  \n[Company Name]  \n[Contact Information]",
